@base = http://localhost:5284/api

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  AUTH FLOW
###  Run 1-3 (register) then 5-7 (login) first.
###  Tokens are auto-captured via # @name.
###  Then run any request below.
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Register Alice
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Alice", "email": "alice@test.com", "password": "Pass123!" }

### 2. Register Bob
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Bob", "email": "bob@test.com", "password": "Pass123!" }

### 3. Register Charlie
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Charlie", "email": "charlie@test.com", "password": "Pass123!" }

### 4. Duplicate email (should fail 409)
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Alice Clone", "email": "alice@test.com", "password": "Pass123!" }

### 5. Login as Alice
# @name loginAlice
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "alice@test.com", "password": "Pass123!" }

### 6. Login as Bob
# @name loginBob
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "bob@test.com", "password": "Pass123!" }

### 7. Login as Charlie
# @name loginCharlie
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "charlie@test.com", "password": "Pass123!" }

### 8. Wrong password (should fail 401)
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "alice@test.com", "password": "WrongPassword!" }

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  COUPON CRUD
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 9. Create SAVE20 (count=5)
POST {{base}}/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "code": "SAVE20", "expirationDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z", "count": 5 }

### 10. Create EXPIRED (past expiration)
POST {{base}}/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "code": "EXPIRED", "expirationDate": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z", "count": 5 }

### 11. Create SINGLE (count=1)
POST {{base}}/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "code": "SINGLE", "expirationDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z", "count": 1 }

### 12. Count=0 (should fail 400)
POST {{base}}/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "code": "SOLDOUT", "expirationDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z", "count": 0 }

### 13. Duplicate code (should fail 409)
POST {{base}}/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "code": "SAVE20", "expirationDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z", "count": 5 }

### 14. Global pool
GET {{base}}/coupons?page=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=code&sortDirection=asc

### 15. Get by code
GET {{base}}/coupons/SAVE20

### 16. Non-existent (should fail 404)
GET {{base}}/coupons/NONEXISTENT

### 17. Alice's own coupons
GET {{base}}/coupons/mine?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}

### 18. Update SAVE20 count → 3
PUT {{base}}/coupons/SAVE20
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "count": 3 }

### 19. Update with Bob's token (should fail 403)
PUT {{base}}/coupons/SAVE20
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "count": 10 }

### 20. Create disposable coupon
POST {{base}}/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "code": "TODELETE", "expirationDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z", "count": 2 }

### 21. Soft delete TODELETE
DELETE {{base}}/coupons/TODELETE
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}

### 22. Verify TODELETE gone (should fail 404)
GET {{base}}/coupons/TODELETE

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  CLAIM FLOW
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 23. Bob claims SAVE20 (count 3→2)
POST {{base}}/claims/SAVE20
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}

### 24. Bob claims again (should fail 409)
POST {{base}}/claims/SAVE20
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}

### 25. Alice claims own coupon (should fail 400)
POST {{base}}/claims/SAVE20
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}

### 26. Claim expired (should fail 410)
POST {{base}}/claims/EXPIRED
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}

### 27. Non-existent (should fail 404)
POST {{base}}/claims/NONEXISTENT
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}

### 28. No auth (should fail 401)
POST {{base}}/claims/SAVE20

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  CLAIM HISTORY
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 29. Bob's history
GET {{base}}/claims?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}

### 30. Alice's history
GET {{base}}/claims?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  CONCURRENCY SETUP
###  Create fresh coupons that NO ONE has claimed yet.
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 31. Create RACE_OVERSELL (count=3) — 5 parallel claims → 3 succeed
POST {{base}}/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "code": "RACE_OVERSELL", "expirationDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z", "count": 3 }

### 32. Create RACE_SPOT (count=1) — 5 parallel claims → 1 succeeds
POST {{base}}/coupons
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAlice.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "code": "RACE_SPOT", "expirationDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z", "count": 1 }

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  RACE: OVERSELL (3 spots, 5 claimants)
###  Fire these 5 requests in PARALLEL.
###  Expected: exactly 3 succeed (200), 2 fail (410 sold out)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 33. Bob claims RACE_OVERSELL (fire with 34-37 in parallel)
POST {{base}}/claims/RACE_OVERSELL
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}

### 34. Charlie claims RACE_OVERSELL (fire with 33, 35-37 in parallel)
POST {{base}}/claims/RACE_OVERSELL
Authorization: Bearer {{loginCharlie.response.body.$.token}}

### 35. Bob claims RACE_OVERSELL again (fire with 33-34, 36-37 in parallel)
POST {{base}}/claims/RACE_OVERSELL
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}

### 36. Charlie claims RACE_OVERSELL again (fire with 33-35, 37 in parallel)
POST {{base}}/claims/RACE_OVERSELL
Authorization: Bearer {{loginCharlie.response.body.$.token}}

### 37. Bob claims RACE_OVERSELL 3rd time (fire with 33-36 in parallel)
POST {{base}}/claims/RACE_OVERSELL
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}                    

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  RACE: SINGLE SPOT (1 spot, 5 claimants)
###  Fire these 5 requests in PARALLEL.
###  Expected: exactly 1 succeeds (200), 4 fail (410 or 409)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 38. Bob claims RACE_SPOT (fire with 39-42 in parallel)
POST {{base}}/claims/RACE_SPOT
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}

### 39. Charlie claims RACE_SPOT (fire with 38, 40-42 in parallel)
POST {{base}}/claims/RACE_SPOT
Authorization: Bearer {{loginCharlie.response.body.$.token}}

### 40. Bob claims RACE_SPOT again (fire with 38-39, 41-42 in parallel)
POST {{base}}/claims/RACE_SPOT
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}

### 41. Charlie claims RACE_SPOT again (fire with 38-40, 42 in parallel)
POST {{base}}/claims/RACE_SPOT
Authorization: Bearer {{loginCharlie.response.body.$.token}}

### 42. Bob claims RACE_SPOT 3rd time (fire with 38-41 in parallel)
POST {{base}}/claims/RACE_SPOT
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────
###  RACE: DUPLICATE PROTECTION
###  Fire these 3 requests in PARALLEL.
###  Same user (Bob), same coupon (RACE_OVERSELL, already claimed at 33).
###  Expected: exactly 1 may succeed (if count left), rest fail (409 already claimed)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────

### 43-45. 3× parallel claim by same user on RACE_OVERSELL
POST {{base}}/claims/RACE_OVERSELL
Authorization: Bearer {{loginBob.response.body.$.token}}
